title: Thom Hartmann Program - December 05 2013
description:
December 05, 2013
The Thom Hartmann Program 

Hour One: Are we seeing a return to Nixon conservatism?  Daniel Rothschild, R Street Institute

Hour Two: Banksters adopt Walmart method of doing business - Mike Papantonio, Ring of Fire Radio / Plus, Geeky Science - dinner shocker...what's in your meat?  

Hour Three: Thom comments on the life of Nelson Mandela - takes your calls.  Plus, a debate on raising the minimum wage. And is "Big Labor" bullying McWorkers?  Tony Katz, Tony Katz Tonight
